{"type": "article", "id": 29856, "title": "“菲董”特别版 NMD 球鞋即将发售，Zara推出芭蕾系列｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-20T04:18:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 341, "name": "运动"}, {"id": 616, "name": "博物馆"}, {"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 11592, "name": "夏季"}, {"id": 13573, "name": "秋冬大片"}, {"id": 25395, "name": "裸色"}, {"id": 27239, "name": "NMD"}, {"id": 30383, "name": "国际羊毛标志大奖赛"}, {"id": 30384, "name": "芭蕾"}, {"id": 30385, "name": "多伦多时装周"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}, {"id": 1802, "name": "Zara"}, {"id": 2744, "name": "IMG"}, {"id": 5139, "name": "Time"}, {"id": 8195, "name": "Banana Republic"}, {"id": 30386, "name": "InStyle"}, {"id": 30387, "name": "Mytheresa"}, {"id": 726, "name": "Pharrell Williams"}, {"id": 17322, "name": "Gigi Hadid"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160720112014qJzv4VpFhKOxTPH7.jpg", "contents": "<h3><b>一些重要的新闻：</b></h3><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Toronto-Fashion-Week-cancelled,714795.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>多伦多时装周将取消</b></a>｜多伦多时装周的主办方：加拿大 IMG 近日宣布将暂停举办多伦多时装周，因缺少当地的支持，2012 年起举办的多伦多时装周是加拿大目前规模最大、北美规模第二（仅次于纽约时装周）的时装发布会。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/denim/calvin-klein-jeans-and-mytheresa-com-do-capsule-collection-10492476/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Calvin Klein 和 Mytheresa.com 推出合作系列</b></a>｜Calvin Klein Jeans 宣布要和奢侈品牌电商 Mytheresa.com 合作推出一个女装胶囊系列——Calvin Klein Jeans Rebel Edge 限量版。包括机车夹克、T 恤、leggings、短裤、超短裙、靴子和水桶包等单品，价格在 88-798 美元之间。近日在 mytheresa.com 网站上发布，9 月 1 日可以在 Calvin Klein Jeans 门店和官网上买到。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/editorial-director-ariel-foxman-departs-instyle-time-inc-10492058/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b><i>InStyle</i> 编辑主任离职</b></a>｜掌舵八年后， 杂志&nbsp;<i>InStyle </i>的编辑主任 Ariel Foxman 宣布将于 8 月 4 日从杂志<i> InStyle</i> 离职，稍后 Time 集团将任命一个过渡期的总编。Ariel Foxman 在 Time 集团任职超过 15 年，掌管 <i>InStyle </i>、<i>StyleWatch</i>，并帮助建立线上版本，今年还领导了<i> InStyle </i>纸质及数码版本的改版。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/gabriela-hearst-and-rochambeau-named-u-s-regional-woolmark-winners-10492555/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>International Woolmark Prize 公布美洲区冠军</b></a>｜国际羊毛标志大奖赛（International Woolmark Prize）近日宣布 Gabriela Hearst 和 Rochambeau 分别获得美洲地区的女装和男装大奖。其它的五个区域为悉尼、伦敦、香港、米兰和孟买，最终全球决赛的冠军将获得 10 万澳币奖金及行业内专家的指导。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>Pharrell Williams 再次与 Adidas 三叶草合作，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/adidas-originals-pharrell-williams-hu-nmd\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hu NMD 系列球鞋即将发售</a>。其中 Hu 代表“人类”（Human Race）。预计 7 月 22 日在“菲董”的 Billionaire Boys Club 旗舰店及一些精选店上市，8 月 25 日起可以在三叶草门店购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720113444R81FYBW5daT6femc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720113440jfBKpQaeYnwIqg7u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720113442WGd8yqs01CIPmD5K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720113436Ha3zcDCJ7KZxkAji.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720113438jHalnwkyhJsZ9gXS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720113438KBgOCeEhWFk5UbRm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607201134410Xhj6IYBmFt2SN7q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>快时尚品牌 Zara 推出一个<a href=\"http://www.whowhatwear.com/zara-ballet-collection/slide4\" rel=\"nofollow\">“芭蕾系列”</a>：<br></p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720103116BYmKk0IzuwtpA7e9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720103116ok3yFGmBs8ehZrQn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720103116CtSTjKoDNdbBqJ6n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720103116itzUwEZGdDvk5cKQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720103116megok0D84SI7jL52.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\">Gigi Hadid 为 Tommy Hilfiger 新香水<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/gigi-hadid-tommy-hilfiger-fragrance-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">“The Girl”拍广告</a>：<br></p><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720105929tQxZGUDEb3INlKh7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.249333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607201058579hH4ilOBqeXz7d1Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.888000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720105857DJ0H2VGimlsgzhZT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/kendall-jenner-fendi-fall-2016-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kendall Jenner 则出镜 Fendi 秋冬季广告</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720110108qSHaZvCGweJtU1dX.jpg\" alt=\"\